                                                                    <td class="life" style="padding:8px; font-color: white; text-align: left; border: 1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204);background-color: #2166a1;"> <span style="color:#ffffff;"><b>YOU CAN MAKE THE DIFFERENCE</b></span></td>
                                                                </tr>
